query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND cct2.kind in ('complete','crew','cast') AND cct1.kind not in ('cast','complete') AND (k.keyword like '%war%' OR k.keyword like '%betrayal%' OR k.keyword like '%action%' OR k.keyword like '%alien%') AND mi_idx.info > '6.0' AND kt.kind in ('tv mini series','movie','episode','video game','video movie','tv movie') AND it2.info in ('book','sound mix','LD dynamic range','weekend gross','alternate versions','opening weekend','nick names','LD number of sides','certificates','production dates','LD official retail price','LD spaciality','LD sound encoding','LD supplement','LD disc format','LD audio quality','color info','top 250 rank') AND t.title not like '%thriller%' AND t.title not like '%thunder%' AND t.title not like '%road%' AND t.title not like '%suit%' AND t.title not like '%star%' AND n.gender in ('f') AND (n.name like '%x%' OR n.name like '%T%' OR n.name like '%o%')
